summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department providing for purchase of right of way necessary for opening and establishing College Way North between Burke Avenue North and North 95th Street and between North 92nd Street and Wallingford Avenue North in the vicinity of North Seattle Community College and for the necessary expenses of the Law and Engineering Departments in connection with such purchase or any subsequent condemnation proceedings, and making an appropriation from the Arterial Development Fund therefor.
